node.text:
Just doesn’t get any better than this in my book! I hung back and took it all in for a good 15 miles while the rest of the boys rode in a tight pack through this stretch of Montana.
The Lolo Run will forever be hard to beat, great group of chopper heads to party with while on a 1400+ mile trip. Thanks Luke @chop_merchandise for the memories of some of the most amazing roads Idaho, Utah and Montana have to offer!
Tune: #danielnorgrenmedband 
Where’s the shine? @tony_medellintattoo
#inviteonly
